{"tid":1979351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［鞭屍系列］坡狗笑港人囤積口罩做法低能","createTime":"2020-04-19T11:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T18:28:25.000Z","uid":83052,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3eabb9ad8f5ca993eae4809f6d5c8ebd6d06da03","tid":1979351,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"「新加坡貿易及工業部長陳振聲向基層領袖閉門分享新加坡政府如何對應武漢病毒的對應措施，錄音不知就裏疑似被流出。當中提及新加坡人不要效法香港人去搶口罩、搶廁紙的「低能」做法，影響疫症後的經濟復甦。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%95%B6%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%AA-why-so-idiot/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%25AA-why-so-idiot%2F&d=BjPUJoueJJBj8huYKMWPWltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=2a89bc5f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2595%25B6%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A1%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2595%25B7%25E5%25B0%258D%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25AA%25AA-why-so-idiot%2F&h=b03fc33a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%95%B6%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E5%B0%8D%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%AA%AA-why-so-idiot/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩個月後...<br />\n「被西方視為抗疫模範的新加坡，疫情持續惡化，單日新增596宗新型冠狀病毒肺炎（新冠肺炎）確診個案，外籍勞工宿舍續成播毒溫床，累積病例達至6,588宗，超越印尼成為東南亞錄得最多宗新冠肺炎確診個案的國家。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2621647/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%8A%A0%E5%9D%A1%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E3%80%91%E6%88%90%E6%9D%B1%E5%8D%97%E4%BA%9E%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A%20%E5%96%AE%E6%97%A5%E5%86%8D%E5%A2%9E%E8%BF%91600%E5%AE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2621647%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%259D%25A